summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department; authorizing an Easement Agreement with the City of Renton, Washington, for road purposes, (South 7th Street) across portions of the 66 foot wide Cedar River Pipeline right-of-way in the Southwest 1/4 of Section 17, Township 23 North, Range 5 East, W.M. and accepting One Thousand Six Hundred and Sixty Four Dollars ($1,664.00) as compensation therefor.
